These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-1::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: yellow, amber, red, ebony, lilac, black
6 different pets are kept: bird, cat, goat, hedgehog, pony, snake
 1. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3
 2. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
 3. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 4. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3
 5. the owner of the goat is the person who likes lilac##1
 6. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
 7. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
 8. the owner of the goat is on the far right##1
 9. the person who likes ebony is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who likes red is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
11. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
12. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |    3     |  4   |       5       |   6   |
| Color   | ebony | black | amber    | yellow | red | lilac |
| Pet        | cat      | snake  | hedgehog | bird | pony          | goat  |

