.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, climbing, handball, weightlifting, rowing, rugby
There are 6 different nationalities: american, argentine, italian, japanese, nigerian, russian
 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 2. the american is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
 3. the japanese is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
 4. the japanese is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
 5. the nigerian is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is the italian##1
 7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is climbing##2
 8. the russian is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 9. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
10. the japanese is on the right of the italian##1
11. the nigerian is on the left or right of the argentine##3
12. the argentine is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
13. the italian is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
14. the italian is on the left or right of the american##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |       3       |    4     |     5     |    6     |
| Sport      | biathlon  | weightlifting     | climbing | handball    | rugby       | rowing  |
| Nationality   | russian | american | italian       | japanese | argentine | nigerian |

