.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-3::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  analyst, dressmaker, electrician, journalist, librarian, writer
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: tulip, iris, zinnia, amaryllis, orchid, poppy
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the analyst##3
2. the librarian is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
3. the analyst is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
4. the electrician is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far right##1
6. the journalist is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
7. the dressmaker is between the journalist and the electrician##2
8. the librarian is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |      3      |     4     |    5     |     6     |
| Job         | journalist | dressmaker | electrician | librarian | analyst  | writer    |
| Flower   | poppy      | zinnia  | orchid  | iris       | tulip | amaryllis |

