.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-4::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: may, july, june, september, november, january
The people have 6 different hobbies: camping, card-games, drawing, fishing, reading, writing
 1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's birthday is in november##2
 9. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5    |       6       |
| Birthday   | july   | january     | november | may        | september   | june |
| Hobby      | camping | reading | drawing  | card-games | writing | fishing       |

