.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-6::.
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, goldfish, turtle, guinea-pig, rat
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: climbing, golf, skateboarding, snowboarding, soccer, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
 2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the owner of the rat##2
 3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 5. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
 6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
 9. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
11. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |   2    |     3     |     4      |      5       |        6        |
| Pet     | dog        | turtle | rat | chinchilla  | goldfish  | guinea-pig |
| Sport   | skateboarding | golf   | climbing  | volleyball | snowboarding | soccer          |

