.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-7::.
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, goat, goldfish, guinea-pig, hedgehog
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: november, february, december, october, may, march
 1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is the owner of the goldfish##1
10. the owner of the goat is between the owner of the goldfish and the person who's birthday is in february##2
11. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |    3     |     4      |   5    |     6      |
| Pet         | hedgehog | goat      | goldfish | guinea-pig | ferret | chinchilla |
| Birthday   | february  | november | may   | march        | december   | october |

