.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-8::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, juice, tea, water
There are 6 different favourite colors: coral, red, azure, white, blue, purple
 1. the person who likes blue is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 3. the person who likes red is the person drinking tea##1
 4. the person who likes coral is the person drinking juice##1
 5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 7. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who likes azure##1
 9. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
10. the person who likes white is the person drinking water##1
11. the person drinking tea is the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2     |   3   |    4     |    5    |     6      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | water     | juice | iced-tea | cola    | tea        |
| Color      | azure   | white | coral | blue   | purple | red |

