.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-9::.
There are 6 different nationalities: australian, brazilian, canadian, german, japanese, spanish
There 6 different types of food: cherry, raspberry, radish, pumpkin, grapefruit, lettuce
 1. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the canadian##1
 2. the canadian is the person eating grapefruit##1
 3. the german is on the left of the japanese##1
 4. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the spanish##3
 5. the person eating raspberry is the german##1
 6. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the spanish##3
 7. the brazilian is the person eating cherry##1
 8. the brazilian is on the right of the japanese##1
 9. the german is between the japanese and the person eating grapefruit##2
10. the person eating lettuce is the spanish##1
11. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the australian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |    5     |     6     |
| Nationality   | australian | spanish | canadian | german   | japanese | brazilian |
| Food           | radish    | lettuce    | grapefruit   | raspberry | pumpkin | cherry      |

