.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-10::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, game, dunhill, dannemann, montecristo, aristoff
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, climbing, parkour, rowing, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
2. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
5. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
7. the game-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
8. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
9. the person who's sport is baseball is between the dunhill-smoker and the person who's sport is climbing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |    3    |    4     |      5      |       6       |
| Cigar   | aristoff  | montecristo | bluemaster     | dannemann    | game | dunhill |
| Sport      | badminton | rowing   | parkour | climbing | baseball    | surfing       |

